# Part 3: Navigation Flow

## Navigation Flow Diagram (Text Representation)

```
Login → Dashboard
Dashboard → Student Profile / Instructor Config
Instructor Config → Run Match
Run Match → Processing (Agent)
Processing → Team Results
Team Results → Analytics Dashboard
Student → Weekly Check-in → Contribution Tracking
```

## Flow Explanation

* Users log in and are routed based on role
* Students submit profiles
* Instructors configure constraints
* Instructors trigger team generation
* Results are displayed with analytics
* Students submit weekly updates

